@{
    ViewBag.Title = "蘆薈清新面膜";
    ViewBag.Title2 = "產品介紹";
    ViewBag.BodyClass = "Products Products_content";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/Layout.cshtml";
}
@section breadcrumb {
<li><a href="~/Products/list">@ViewBag.Title2</a></li>
}

<h3 class="title">@ViewBag.Title</h3>

<dl class="pro-intro list-unstyled row">
    <dt>
        <img src="~/Content/images/Products/pro5/pic.jpg" alt="">
        <article class="point">
            <h5 class="title">水針布：</h5>
            <p>敷完後面膜紙不會乾透，是一種環保產品，具有防潮、透氣柔韌、質輕等特點，能吸附大量精華液，且不易滴落。</p>
        </article>
    </dt>
    <dd>
        <article class="intro">
            <h5 class="title">蘆薈的潤澤保濕度，能讓肌膚回復天然的光澤，清涼保濕安定肌膚，減少油光現象，舒緩曬後不適感，讓皮膚清新粉嫩。</h5>
            <ul class="ingredient list-unstyled">
                <li><strong>Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice 蘆薈萃取液</strong></li>
                <li>Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract 小黃瓜萃取液</li>
                <li>Menthol 薄荷腦</li>
                <li>Sodium Hyaluronate 玻尿酸</li>
                <li>Chlorella Vulgaris Extract 細球藻萃取液</li>
            </ul>
            <ol class="feature list-inline row">
                <li class="col-6 col-xxs-12">
                    <figure>
                        <img src="~/Content/images/Products/pro5/pic2.jpg" alt="">
                        <figcaption>蘆薈萃取液</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </li>
                <li class="col-6 col-xxs-12">
                    <figure>
                        <img src="~/Content/images/Products/pro5/pic3.jpg" alt="">
                        <figcaption>細球藻萃取液</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </article>
    </dd>
</dl>

<section class="pro-detail">
    <h4 class="title">Product Detail</h4>

    <h5 class="title">主成份 Featured Ingredients</h5>
    <ol class="feature list-inline row">
        <li class="col-6 col-xs-12">
            <h6 class="title">Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice 蘆薈萃取液</h6>
            <figure>
                <img src="~/Content/images/Products/pro5/pic2-2.jpg" alt="">
                <figcaption>美國Aloecorp經專業製成技術製造成高濃度蘆薈多醣粉，擁有美國USDA有機認證，延緩肌膚的老化，具高保濕性，並可當作一個生物載體，幫助滲透和其他生物活性成分的吸收。</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </li>
        <li class="col-6 col-xs-12">
            <h6 class="title">Chlorella Vulgaris Extract 細球藻萃取液</h6>
            <figure>
                <img src="~/Content/images/Products/pro5/pic3-2.jpg" alt="">
                <figcaption>維持肌膚水潤彈力，同時防護肌膚抵抗外在環境刺激。</figcaption>
            </figure>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h5 class="title">使用方式 How to Use</h5>
    <ol class="steps list-inline row">
        <li class="col-3 col-xs-12">
            <figure>
                <img src="~/Content/images/Products/step1.jpg" alt="">
            </figure>
            <em>清潔卸妝後，將臉部肌膚擦拭乾淨，輕拍化妝水。</em>
        </li>
        <li class="col-3 col-xs-12">
            <figure>
                <img src="~/Content/images/Products/step2.jpg" alt="">
            </figure>
            <em>取出一片面膜，敷貼全臉。</em>
        </li>
        <li class="col-3 col-xs-12">
            <figure>
                <img src="~/Content/images/Products/step3.jpg" alt="">
            </figure>
            <em>停敷約 15-20 分鐘。</em>
        </li>
        <li class="col-3 col-xs-12">
            <figure>
                <img src="~/Content/images/Products/step4.jpg" alt="">
            </figure>
            <em>取下後可再擦上精華液或乳液/霜。</em>
        </li>
    </ol>

